<h2 class="bold font-l">Little Bear - Under the covers</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Little Bear and his parents have some fun with one another when the tyke tries to help them get rid of some &quot;bed bugs&quot;. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FriendlyTickleTorture" class='trope-example-link'>Friendly Tickle Torture</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
